Retrieve COVID-19 data for all locations at an administrative level.

Source: R/getByAdmnLevel.R
getByAdmnLevel.Rd

Retrieve up-to-date COVID-19 data from outbreak.info for all locations at a given administrative level.

getByAdmnLevel(admin_level, ...)

Arguments

admin_level:

an integer representing an administrative level (World Bank regions = -1, countries = 0, states/provinces = 1, metropolitan areas = 1.5, counties = 2)

Value

dataframe

Examples

getByAdmnLevel(-1)
